TM PURNCESS raced while three wide towards the back of the pack, was urging on the turn to rally in the upper stretch but did not make a difference in the end. AL M raced in the middle of the field from the inside, then made a mild bid in the home stretch and had no impact in the end. UPTOWN LADY ARABELLA stalked the pace from the inside, settled back in the late backstretch then lacked rally in the home stretch. RB MUNCHIE set the pace into the first turn while two wide, then gave way for the lead into the turn then continued to flatten out in the stretch. RB MAMA WINGATE settled inside and was no threat. WMA TORCH LIGHT was unhurried early and no factor. KD DERBY GIRL chased the pace early from the three path then was done after the half.
